<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LMS Account Activation</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Welcome to LMS!</h1>
            <div class="email-body">
                <p>Hello <%= user.name %></p>
                <p>Thank you for registering with LMS, To activate your accout, please use the following activation code: </p>
                <h2><%= activationCode %></h2>
                <p>Please enter this code on the activation code within the next 5 minutes</p>
                <p>If you did not register for an LMS, please ignore this email.</p>
                <div class="email-footer">
                    <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:support@LMS.com">support@LMS.com</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>